<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      tal:omit-tag="textual">
  <head tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <title tal:omit-tag="textual">Your Provider Account Has Been Activated</title>
  </head>
  <body tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <h1 tal:omit-tag="textual">
      Activation of Your Provider Account on <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain Name</span>
    </h1>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">
      Hello<span tal:replace="user" tal:condition="exists:user" tal:omit-tag="textual">Provider Name</span>,
    </p>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">
      Your registration as a <strong>Provider</strong> on our platform
      <a tal:attributes="href site_url"><span tal:replace="site_url">Platform URL</span></a>
      has been successfully completed.
    </p>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">
      You now have access to the management interface allowing you to view and modify
      the attributes of members for whom you have been granted modification rights.
    </p>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">
      If you have any questions or encounter issues, feel free to contact our support team.
    </p>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for your collaboration.</p>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Best regards,</p>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">
      The team of <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain Name</span>
    </p>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual" tal:content="organization_details">Organization details</p>
  </body>
</html>
